{
  "name": "agentheld-mesh",
  "doc": "Three-router full mesh under AgentHeld (controller) custody: each node registers only its public key, the rendered [Interface] PrivateKey is PRIVATEKEY_PLACEHOLDER (zero-knowledge custody, principle P2), and no private key reaches the bundle. Exercises the controller render path's placeholder/discard-private semantics across multiple peers per node.",
